<p data-start="228" data-end="353">Based on what you've already worked on (Excel dashboard and data analytics), I'd recommend these projects in order of impact:</p>
<h3 data-start="355" data-end="413">1. Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard ⭐ (Must Have)</h3>
