</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1943" data-end="2083">That combination shows experience with business reporting, HR metrics, and customer analytics—areas commonly encountered in analytics roles.</p>
<h2 data-start="2085" data-end="2128">Make each project follow this structure:</h2>
<ul data-start="2130" data-end="2255">
