s="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="236">Excellent choice. A <strong data-start="20" data-end="61">Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard</strong> is one of the strongest projects for a Measure &amp; Reporting Analytics role at Accenture because it demonstrates reporting, KPI tracking, trend analysis, and business insights.</p>
<h2 data-start="238" data-end="254">Project Title</h2>
<p data-start="255" data-end="296"><strong data-start="255" data-end="296">Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard</strong></p>
<h2 data-start="298" data-end="317">Business Problem</h2>
<p data-start="318" data-end="499">A retail company wants to analyze its sales performance across different regions, products, and customer segments to identify opportunities for increasing revenue and profitability.</p>
<h2 data-start="501" data-end="509">Tools</h2>
<ul data-start="510" data-end="606">
<li data-start="510" data-end="533">
<p data-start="512" data-end="533">Excel (Data Cleaning)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="562">
<p data-start="536" data-end="562">SQL Server (Data Analysis)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="563" data-end="585">
<p data-start="565" data-end="585">Power BI (Dashboard)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="586" data-end="606">
<p data-start="588" data-end="606">GitHub (Portfolio)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="608" data-end="703">Since you've already installed SQL Server and SSMS, this is a great chance to practice SQL too.</p>
<hr data-start="705" data-end="708">
<h2 data-start="710" data-end="735">Skills You'll Showcase</h2>
<ul data-start="736" data-end="857">
<li data-start="736" data-end="751">
<p data-start="738" data-end="751">Data Cleaning</p>
</li>
<li data-start="752" data-end="765">
<p data-start="754" data-end="765">SQL Queries</p>
</li>
<li data-start="766" data-end="781">
<p data-start="768" data-end="781">Data Modeling</p>
</li>
<li data-start="782" data-end="797">
<p data-start="784" data-end="797">KPI Reporting</p>
</li>
<li data-start="798" data-end="816">
<p data-start="800" data-end="816">Dashboard Design</p>
</li>
<li data-start="817" data-end="836">
<p data-start="819" data-end="836">Business Insights</p>
</li>
<li data-start="837" data-end="857">
<p data-start="839" data-end="857">Data Visualization</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="859" data-end="862">
<h2 data-start="864" data-end="874">Dataset</h2>
<p data-start="876" data-end="969">Use the <strong data-start="884" data-end="905">Sample Superstore</strong> dataset. It is widely used for analytics practice and includes:</p>
<ul data-start="970" data-end="1128">
<li data-start="970" data-end="980">
<p data-start="972" data-end="980">Order ID</p>
</li>
<li data-start="981" data-end="993">
<p data-start="983" data-end="993">Order Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="994" data-end="1005">
<p data-start="996" data-end="1005">Ship Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1006" data-end="1021">
<p data-start="1008" data-end="1021">Customer Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1022" data-end="1031">
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1031">Segment</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1032" data-end="1040">
<p data-start="1034" data-end="1040">Region</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1041" data-end="1048">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1048">State</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1049" data-end="1059">
<p data-start="1051" data-end="1059">Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1060" data-end="1074">
<p data-start="1062" data-end="1074">Sub-Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1075" data-end="1089">
<p data-start="1077" data-end="1089">Product Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1090" data-end="1097">
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1097">Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1098" data-end="1108">
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1108">Quantity</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1109" data-end="1119">
<p data-start="1111" data-end="1119">Discount</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1120" data-end="1128">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1128">Profit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1130" data-end="1133">
<h2 data-start="1135" data-end="1159">Data Cleaning (Excel)</h2>
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1182">Clean the dataset by:</p>
<ul data-start="1183" data-end="1350">
<li data-start="1183" data-end="1204">
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1204">Removing duplicates</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1205" data-end="1230">
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1230">Handling missing values</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1231" data-end="1258">
<p data-start="1233" data-end="1258">Standardizing date format</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1259" data-end="1280">
<p data-start="1261" data-end="1280">Checking data types</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1281" data-end="1350">
<p data-start="1283" data-end="1350">Correcting inconsistent text (e.g., capitalization or extra spaces)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1352" data-end="1355">
<h2 data-start="1357" data-end="1372">SQL Analysis</h2>
<p data-start="1374" data-end="1443">Import the cleaned data into SQL Server and practice queries such as:</p>
<ol data-start="1445" data-end="1777">
<li data-start="1445" data-end="1459">
<p data-start="1448" data-end="1459">Total Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1460" data-end="1475">
<p data-start="1463" data-end="1475">Total Profit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1476" data-end="1491">
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1491">Total Orders</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1492" data-end="1514">
<p data-start="1495" data-end="1514">Average Order Value</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1515" data-end="1537">
<p data-start="1518" data-end="1537">Monthly Sales Trend</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1538" data-end="1565">
<p data-start="1541" data-end="1565">Top 10 Products by Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1566" data-end="1594">
<p data-start="1569" data-end="1594">Top 10 Products by Profit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1595" data-end="1615">
<p data-start="1598" data-end="1615">Region-wise Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1616" data-end="1638">
<p data-start="1619" data-end="1638">Category-wise Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1639" data-end="1661">
<p data-start="1643" data-end="1661">Segment-wise Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1662" data-end="1683">
<p data-start="1666" data-end="1683">State-wise Profit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1684" data-end="1713">
<p data-start="1688" data-end="1713">Highest Discount Products</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1714" data-end="1743">
<p data-start="1718" data-end="1743">Profit Margin by Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1744" data-end="1777">
<p data-start="1748" data-end="1777">Sales Growth Month-over-Month</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1779" data-end="1782">
<h2 data-start="1784" data-end="1804">KPIs for Power BI</h2>
<p data-start="1806" data-end="1828">Display KPI cards for:</p>
<ul data-start="1829" data-end="1910">
<li data-start="1829" data-end="1842">
<p data-start="1831" data-end="1842">Total Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1843" data-end="1857">
<p data-start="1845" data-end="1857">Total Profit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1858" data-end="1872">
<p data-start="1860" data-end="1872">Total Orders</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1873" data-end="1894">
<p data-start="1875" data-end="1894">Average Order Value</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1895" data-end="1910">
<p data-start="1897" data-end="1910">Profit Margin</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1912" data-end="1915">
<h2 data-start="1917" data-end="1937">Dashboard Visuals</h2>
<p data-start="1939" data-end="1947">Include:</p>
<ul data-start="1948" data-end="2221">
<li data-start="1948" data-end="1982">
<p data-start="1950" data-end="1982">Line Chart → Monthly Sales Trend</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1983" data-end="2014">
<p data-start="1985" data-end="2014">Bar Chart → Sales by Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2015" data-end="2044">
<p data-start="2017" data-end="2044">Bar Chart → Sales by Region</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2045" data-end="2067">
<p data-start="2047" data-end="2067">Map → Sales by State</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2068" data-end="2104">
<p data-start="2070" data-end="2104">Pie/Donut Chart → Sales by Segment</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2105" data-end="2139">
<p data-start="2107" data-end="2139">Tree Map → Sales by Sub-Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2140" data-end="2165">
<p data-start="2142" data-end="2165">Table → Top 10 Products</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2166" data-end="2221">
<p data-start="2168" data-end="2176">Slicers:</p>
<ul data-start="2179" data-end="2221">
<li data-start="2179" data-end="2185">
<p data-start="2181" data-end="2185">Year</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2188" data-end="2196">
<p data-start="2190" data-end="2196">Region</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2199" data-end="2209">
<p data-start="2201" data-end="2209">Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2212" data-end="2221">
<p data-start="2214" data-end="2221">Segment</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2223" data-end="2226">
<h2 data-start="2228" data-end="2248">Business Insights</h2>
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2259">Examples:</p>
<ul data-start="2260" data-end="2544">
<li data-start="2260" data-end="2306">
<p data-start="2262" data-end="2306">The West region generated the highest sales.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2307" data-end="2359">
<p data-start="2309" data-end="2359">Technology products had the highest profit margin.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2360" data-end="2424">
<p data-start="2362" data-end="2424">Office Supplies had high sales volume but lower profitability.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2425" data-end="2491">
<p data-start="2427" data-end="2491">A small number of products contributed a large share of revenue.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2492" data-end="2544">
<p data-start="2494" data-end="2544">High discounts were associated with lower profits.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2546" data-end="2549">
<h2 data-start="2551" data-end="2569">Recommendations</h2>
<ul data-start="2571" data-end="2768">
<li data-start="2571" data-end="2615">
<p data-start="2573" data-end="2615">Focus marketing on high-profit categories.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2616" data-end="2668">
<p data-start="2618" data-end="2668">Reduce excessive discounts on low-margin products.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2669" data-end="2712">
<p data-start="2671" data-end="2712">Increase inventory for top-selling items.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2713" data-end="2768">
<p data-start="2715" data-end="2768">Improve sales strategies in lower-performing regions.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2770" data-end="2773">
<h2 data-start="2775" data-end="2805">GitHub Repository Structure</h2>
