<h2 data-start="3036" data-end="3057">Resume Description</h2>
<p data-start="3059" data-end="3100"><strong data-start="3059" data-end="3100">Sales Performance Analytics Dashboard</strong></p>
<ul data-start="3101" data-end="3470">
<li data-start="3101" data-end="3172">
<p data-start="3103" data-end="3172">Cleaned and transformed retail sales data using Excel and SQL Server.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3173" data-end="3261">
<p data-start="3175" data-end="3261">Analyzed sales, profit, customer segments, and regional performance using SQL queries.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3262" data-end="3358">
<p data-start="3264" data-end="3358">Developed an interactive Power BI dashboard with KPI cards, trend analysis, maps, and slicers.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3359" data-end="3470">
<p data-start="3361" data-end="3470">Identified key business insights and provided recommendations to improve sales performance and profitability.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3472" data-end="3475">
<p data-start="3477" data-end="3656">This project is suitable for an entry-level analytics portfolio because it covers the full workflow: data cleaning, SQL analysis, dashboard creation, and business recommendations.</p>
<p data-start="3658" data-end="3786" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Once you've finished this one, you can move on to an HR Analytics Dashboard to show experience with a different business domain.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg