iv></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section></div><div class="" data-turn-id-container="request-WEB:572b3fa9-0061-4161-af2a-d9bbd7c48a0e-3" data-is-intersecting="true"><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto R6Vx5W_threadScrollVars scroll-mb-[calc(var(--scroll-root-safe-area-inset-bottom,0px)+var(--thread-response-height))] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:572b3fa9-0061-4161-af2a-d9bbd7c48a0e-3" data-turn-id-container="request-WEB:572b3fa9-0061-4161-af2a-d9bbd7c48a0e-3" data-testid="conversation-turn-8" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div data-conversation-screenshot-content="" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="fc2eead3-d098-436c-946e-bca6a46b52b8" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert wrap-break-word w-full dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="117">That's completely fine. Since you're trying to <strong data-start="47" data-end="76">apply as soon as possible</strong>, don't wait until you have 3–4 projects.</p>
<p data-start="119" data-end="252">For an <strong data-start="126" data-end="169">Accenture Measure &amp; Reporting Analytics</strong> application, <strong data-start="183" data-end="251">one well-executed project is better than several incomplete ones</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="254" data-end="291">Here's what I'd do in your situation:</p>
<ol data-start="293" data-end="645">
<li data-start="293" data-end="378">
<p data-start="296" data-end="378"><strong data-start="296" data-end="353">Finish one strong Sales Performance Analytics project</strong> (1–2 days if you focus).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="379" data-end="506">
<p data-start="382" data-end="407">Upload it to GitHub with:</p>
<ul data-start="411" data-end="506">
<li data-start="411" data-end="420">
<p data-start="413" data-end="420">Dataset</p>
</li>
<li data-start="424" data-end="436">
<p data-start="426" data-end="436">SQL script</p>
</li>
<li data-start="440" data-end="468">
<p data-start="442" data-end="468">Power BI dashboard (.pbix)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="472" data-end="494">
<p data-start="474" data-end="494">Dashboard screenshot</p>
</li>
<li data-start="498" data-end="506">
<p data-start="500" data-end="506">README</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="507" data-end="545">
<p data-start="510" data-end="545">Add it to your resume and LinkedIn.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="546" data-end="576">
<p data-start="549" data-end="576">Start applying immediately.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="577" data-end="645">
<p data-start="580" data-end="645">Build additional projects while you're applying and interviewing.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="647" data-end="799">Recruiters understand that fresh graduates won't always have a large portfolio. They care more about whether you can demonstrate the analytics workflow.</p>
<h3 data-start="801" data-end="828">Since you already have:</h3>
<ul data-start="829" data-end="884">
<li data-start="829" data-end="838">
<p data-start="831" data-end="838">✅ Excel</p>
</li>
<li data-start="839" data-end="860">
<p data-start="841" data-end="860">✅ SQL Server &amp; SSMS</p>
</li>
<li data-start="861" data-end="873">
<p data-start="863" data-end="873">✅ Power BI</p>
</li>
<li data-start="874" data-end="884">
<p data-start="876" data-end="884">✅ GitHub</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="886" data-end="922">You already have the tools you need.</p>
<h3 data-start="924" data-end="973">I can help you make this project much faster.</h3>
<p data-start="975" data-end="1062">Instead of spending days figuring everything out yourself, I'll guide you step by step:</p>
<ul data-start="1064" data-end="1314">
<li data-start="1064" data-end="1095">
<p data-start="1066" data-end="1095">Step 1: Download the dataset.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1096" data-end="1124">
<p data-start="1098" data-end="1124">Step 2: Clean it in Excel.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1125" data-end="1161">
<p data-start="1127" data-end="1161">Step 3: Import it into SQL Server.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1162" data-end="1202">
<p data-start="1164" data-end="1202">Step 4: I'll give you the SQL queries.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1203" data-end="1242">
<p data-start="1205" data-end="1242">Step 5: Build the Power BI dashboard.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1243" data-end="1314">
<p data-start="1245" data-end="1314">Step 6: I'll help you write the GitHub README and resume description.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1425">This way, you can realistically have a portfolio-ready project in <strong data-start="1382" data-end="1394">1–2 days</strong> and start applying right away.</p>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1661" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Given your goal of applying quickly, I wouldn't delay applications waiting for multiple projects. A polished single project, combined with your existing Cafe Sales Analysis, is enough to start applying for entry-level analytics roles.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="t