<p data-start="271" data-end="291"><strong data-start="271" data-end="291">Tools we'll use:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="292" data-end="347">
<li data-start="292" data-end="301">
<p data-start="294" data-end="301">✅ Excel</p>
</li>
<li data-start="302" data-end="323">
<p data-start="304" data-end="323">✅ SQL Server + SSMS</p>
</li>
<li data-start="324" data-end="336">
<p data-start="326" data-end="336">✅ Power BI</p>
</li>
