<hr data-start="349" data-end="352">
<h1 data-start="354" data-end="386">Phase 1: Data Cleaning (Excel)</h1>
<h2 data-start="388" data-end="411">Step 1: Open the CSV</h2>
<p data-start="413" data-end="455">Open <strong data-start="418" data-end="445">Sample - Superstore.csv</strong> in Excel.</p>
<hr data-start="457" data-end="460">
<h2 data-start="462" data-end="496">Step 2: Convert it into a Table</h2>
<ol data-start="498" data-end="630">
<li data-start="498" data-end="532">
<p data-start="501" data-end="532">Click anywhere inside the data.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="533" data-end="555">
<p data-start="536" data-end="555">Press <strong data-start="542" data-end="554">Ctrl + A</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="556" data-end="578">
<p data-start="559" data-end="578">Press <strong data-start="565" data-end="577">Ctrl + T</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="579" data-end="613">
<p data-start="582" data-end="613">Check <strong data-start="588" data-end="612">My table has headers</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="614" data-end="630">
<p data-start="617" data-end="630">Click <strong data-start="623" data-end="629">OK</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="632" data-end="635">
<h2 data-start="637" data-end="672">Step 3: Check for Missing Values</h2>
<p data-start="674" data-end="691">For every column:</p>
<ol data-start="693" data-end="745">
<li data-start="693" data-end="719">
<p data-start="696" data-end="719">Click the filter arrow.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="720" data-end="745">
<p data-start="723" data-end="745">Look for <strong data-start="732" data-end="744">(Blanks)</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="747" data-end="821">If there are no blanks, great. If there are, note which columns have them.</p>
<hr data-start="823" data-end="826">
<h2 data-start="828" data-end="859">Step 4: Check for Duplicates</h2>
<p data-start="861" data-end="877">Select all data.</p>
<p data-start="879" data-end="885">Go to:</p>
<p data-start="887" data-end="915"><strong data-start="887" data-end="915">Data → Remove Duplicates</strong></p>
<p data-start="917" data-end="948">Do <strong data-start="920" data-end="927">not</strong> remove anything yet.</p>
<p data-start="950" data-end="1007">If Excel says <strong data-start="964" data-end="993">No duplicate values found</strong>, that's fine.</p>
<hr data-start="1009" data-end="1012">
<h2 data-start="1014" data-end="1042">Step 5: Check Date Format</h2>
<p data-start="1044" data-end="1052">Columns:</p>
<ul data-start="1054" data-end="1078">
<li data-start="1054" data-end="1066">
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1066">Order Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1067" data-end="1078">
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1078">Ship Date</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1080" data-end="1101">They should look like</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1103" data-end="1121"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>01-02-2023</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1123" data-end="1125">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1127" data-end="1143"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>1/2/2023</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1145" data-end="1207">Both are acceptable as long as Excel recognizes them as dates.</p>
<hr data-start="1209" data-end="1212">
<h2 data-start="1214" data-end="1241">Step 6: Check Data Types</h2>
<p data-start="1243" data-end="1267">These should be numbers:</p>
<ul data-start="1269" data-end="1307">
<li data-start="1269" data-end="1276">
<p data-start="1271" data-end="1276">Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1277" data-end="1287">
<p data-start="1279" data-end="1287">Quantity</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1288" data-end="1298">
<p data-start="1290" data-end="1298">Discount</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1299" data-end="1307">
<p data-start="1301" data-end="1307">Profit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1309" data-end="1371">They should <strong data-start="1321" data-end="1328">not</strong> have green triangles or be stored as text.</p>
<hr data-start="1373" data-end="1376">
<h2 data-start="1378" data-end="1393">Step 7: Save</h2>
<p data-start="1395" data-end="1402">Save as</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1404" data-end="1435"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Superstore_Cleaned.xlsx</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1437" data-end="1440">
<h1 data-start="1442" data-end="1463">Phase 2: SQL Server</h1>
<h2 data-start="1465" data-end="1485">Step 8: Open SSMS</h2>
