<hr data-start="107" data-end="110">
<h1 data-start="112" data-end="151">Step 1: Convert the data into a Table</h1>
<ol data-start="153" data-end="311">
<li data-start="153" data-end="190">
<p data-start="156" data-end="190">Click anywhere inside the dataset.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="191" data-end="236">
<p data-start="194" data-end="236">Press <strong data-start="200" data-end="212">Ctrl + A</strong> to select all the data.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="237" data-end="259">
<p data-start="240" data-end="259">Press <strong data-start="246" data-end="258">Ctrl + T</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="260" data-end="294">
<p data-start="263" data-end="294">Check <strong data-start="269" data-end="293">My table has headers</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="295" data-end="311">
<p data-start="298" data-end="311">Click <strong data-start="304" data-end="310">OK</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="313" data-end="370"><strong data-start="313" data-end="322">Done?</strong> Tell me "Done" and we'll move to the next step.</p>
<hr data-start="372" data-end="375">
<h1 data-start="377" data-end="411">Step 2: Check for Missing Values</h1>
<p data-start="413" data-end="467">We'll check if any important columns have blank cells.</p>
<ol data-start="469" data-end="658">
<li data-start="469" data-end="525">
<p data-start="472" data-end="525">Click the filter dropdown in the <strong data-start="505" data-end="517">Order ID</strong> column.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="526" data-end="557">
<p data-start="529" data-end="557">See if <strong data-start="536" data-end="548">(Blanks)</strong> appears.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="558" data-end="658">
<p data-start="561" data-end="586">Repeat for these columns:</p>
<ul data-start="590" data-end="658">
<li data-start="590" data-end="602">
<p data-start="592" data-end="602">Order Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="606" data-end="621">
<p data-start="608" data-end="621">Customer Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="625" data-end="635">
<p data-start="627" data-end="635">Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="639" data-end="646">
<p data-start="641" data-end="646">Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="650" data-end="658">
<p data-start="652" data-end="658">Profit</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="660" data-end="726">If <strong data-start="663" data-end="675">(Blanks)</strong> doesn't appear, that column has no missing values.</p>
<p data-start="728" data-end="743">👉 <strong data-start="731" data-end="743">Tell me:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="744" data-end="779">
<li data-start="744" data-end="779">
<p data-start="746" data-end="779">Did you find any blanks? (Yes/No)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="781" data-end="784">
<h1 data-start="786" data-end="816">Step 3: Check for Duplicates</h1>
<ol data-start="818" data-end="956">
<li data-start="818" data-end="849">
<p data-start="821" data-end="849">Click anywhere in the table.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="850" data-end="876">
<p data-start="853" data-end="876">Go to the <strong data-start="863" data-end="871">Data</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="877" data-end="908">
<p data-start="880" data-end="908">Click <strong data-start="886" data-end="907">Remove Duplicates</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="909" data-end="939">
<p data-start="912" data-end="939">Leave all columns selected.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="940" data-end="956">
<p data-start="943" data-end="956">Click <strong data-start="949" data-end="955">OK</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="958" data-end="985">Excel will tell you either:</p>
<ul data-start="986" data-end="1055">
<li data-start="986" data-end="1016">
<p data-start="988" data-end="1016">"No duplicate values found."</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1017" data-end="1055">
<p data-start="1019" data-end="1055">Or how many duplicates were removed.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1057" data-end="1105">👉 <strong data-start="1060" data-end="1105">Tell me exactly what message Excel shows.</strong></p>
<blockquote data-start="1107" data-end="1258">
<p data-start="1109" data-end="1258"><strong data-start="1109" data-end="1118">Note:</strong> If you're worried about removing data, you can save a copy of the file first (<code data-start="1197" data-end="1222">Superstore_Cleaned.xlsx</code>) and perform this step on the copy.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1260" data-end="1263">
<p data-start="1265" data-end="1282">Once you tell me:</p>
<ol data-start="1283" data-end="1356">
<li data-start="1283" data-end="1319">
<p data-start="1286" data-end="1319">Whether there are missing values.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1320" data-end="1356">
<p data-start="1323" data-end="1356">What Excel says about duplicates.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1358" data-end="1437" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">We'll continue to checking data types and then import the data into SQL Server.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="tex