<h2 data-start="124" data-end="162">Method 1 (Recommended): Use Filters</h2>
<p data-start="164" data-end="201">After converting the data to a table:</p>
<ol data-start="203" data-end="476">
<li data-start="203" data-end="276">
<p data-start="206" data-end="276">Click the ▼ arrow in a column header (for example, <strong data-start="257" data-end="274">Customer Name</strong>).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="277" data-end="332">
<p data-start="280" data-end="332">Scroll all the way to the bottom of the filter list.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="333" data-end="397">
<p data-start="336" data-end="397">If you see <strong data-start="347" data-end="359">(Blanks)</strong>, that column contains missing values.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="398" data-end="476">
<p data-start="401" data-end="476">If <strong data-start="404" data-end="416">(Blanks)</strong> is <strong data-start="420" data-end="427">not</strong> listed, there are no blank cells in that column.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="478" data-end="523">You only need to check the important columns:</p>
<ul data-start="524" data-end="591">
<li data-start="524" data-end="534">
<p data-start="526" data-end="534">Order ID</p>
</li>
<li data-start="535" data-end="547">
<p data-start="537" data-end="547">Order Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="548" data-end="563">
<p data-start="550" data-end="563">Customer Name</p>
</li>
<li data-start="564" data-end="574">
<p data-start="566" data-end="574">Category</p>
</li>
<li data-start="575" data-end="582">
<p data-start="577" data-end="582">Sales</p>
</li>
<li data-start="583" data-end="591">
<p data-start="585" data-end="591">Profit</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="593" data-end="596">
<h2 data-start="598" data-end="638">Method 2 (Even Faster): Go To Special</h2>
<ol data-start="640" data-end="781">
<li data-start="640" data-end="682">
<p data-start="643" data-end="682">Select the entire table (<strong data-start="668" data-end="680">Ctrl + A</strong>).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="683" data-end="717">
<p data-start="686" data-end="717">Press <strong data-start="692" data-end="698">F5</strong> (or <strong data-start="703" data-end="715">Ctrl + G</strong>).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="718" data-end="742">
<p data-start="721" data-end="742">Click <strong data-start="727" data-end="741">Special...</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="743" data-end="764">
<p data-start="746" data-end="764">Select <strong data-start="753" data-end="763">Blanks</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="765" data-end="781">
<p data-start="768" data-end="781">Click <strong data-start="774" data-end="780">OK</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="783" data-end="915">If Excel selects cells, those are blank cells. If it says <strong data-start="841" data-end="866">"No cells were found"</strong>, there are no blank cells in the selected range.</p>
<hr data-start="917" data-end="920">
<h2 data-start="922" data-end="980">Since you're using the well-known Superstore dataset...</h2>
<p data-start="982" data-end="1015">In most versions of this dataset:</p>
<ul data-start="1016" data-end="1105">
<li data-start="1016" data-end="1060">
<p data-start="1018" data-end="1060">✅ There are usually <strong data-start="1038" data-end="1059">no missing values</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1061" data-end="1105">
<p data-start="1063" data-end="1105">✅ There are usually <strong data-start="1083" data-end="1104">no duplicate rows</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1107" data-end="1170">So if you don't find any blanks or duplicates, that's expected.</p>
<h3 data-start="1172" data-end="1197">Let's move on quickly</h3>
<p data-start="1199" data-end="1317">Instead of spending too much time checking every column, let's verify the dataset in a few minutes and proceed to SQL.</p>
<p data-start="1319" data-end="1331"><strong data-start="1319" data-end="1331">Tell me:</strong></p>
<ol data-start="1332" data-end="1437" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-start="1332" data-end="1382">
<p data-start="1335" data-end="1382">Did you convert the data into a table? (Yes/No)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1383" data-end="1437" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="1386" data-end="1437" data-is-last-node="">Are you using <strong data-start="1400" data-end="1413">Excel 365</strong> or <strong data-start="1417" data-end="1436">Excel 2021/2019</strong>?</p>
</li>
</ol></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button type="button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-surface-hover rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" 