<hr data-start="734" data-end="737">
<h1 data-start="739" data-end="774">🎯 Next Phase: Power BI Dashboard</h1>
<p data-start="776" data-end="814">We'll create a professional dashboard.</p>
<h2 data-start="816" data-end="848">Step 1: Open Power BI Desktop</h2>
<p data-start="850" data-end="880">Tell me when Power BI is open.</p>
<hr data-start="882" data-end="885">
<h2 data-start="887" data-end="906">Step 2: Get Data</h2>
<ol data-start="908" data-end="978">
<li data-start="908" data-end="930">
<p data-start="911" data-end="930">Click <strong data-start="917" data-end="929">Get Data</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="931" data-end="956">
<p data-start="934" data-end="956">Choose <strong data-start="941" data-end="955">SQL Server</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="957" data-end="978">
<p data-start="960" data-end="978">Click <strong data-start="966" data-end="977">Connect</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="980" data-end="1003">You'll see this window:</p>
<ul data-start="1005" data-end="1043">
<li data-start="1005" data-end="1017">
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1017"><strong data-start="1007" data-end="1017">Server</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1018" data-end="1043">
<p data-start="1020" data-end="1043"><strong data-start="1020" data-end="1043">Database (optional)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1045" data-end="1055">Enter:</h3>
<p data-start="1057" data-end="1068"><strong data-start="1057" data-end="1068">Server:</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1069" data-end="1097"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Your SQL Server name</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1099" data-end="1112"><strong data-start="1099" data-end="1112">Database:</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1113" data-end="1133"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-c74d0474.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>SuperstoreDB</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
