<hr data-start="1210" data-end="1213">
<h2 data-start="1215" data-end="1240">Step 3: Authentication</h2>
<p data-start="1242" data-end="1249">Choose:</p>
<ul data-start="1251" data-end="1293">
<li data-start="1251" data-end="1293">
<p data-start="1253" data-end="1293"><strong data-start="1253" data-end="1264">Windows</strong> authentication (the default)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1295" data-end="1318">Then click <strong data-start="1306" data-end="1317">Connect</strong>.</p>
