<p data-start="1392" data-end="1437">Tick the checkbox next to <strong data-start="1418" data-end="1436">dbo.Superstore</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1439" data-end="1454">Click <strong data-start="1445" data-end="1453">Load</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1456" data-end="1459">
<h2 data-start="1461" data-end="1487">Step 5: Verify the data</h2>
<p data-start="1489" data-end="1529">Once loaded, you should see fields like:</p>
<ul data-start="1531" data-end="1613">
<li data-start="1531" data-end="1543">
<p data-start="1533" data-end="1543">Order_Date</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1544" data-end="1551">
