<h1 data-start="1620" data-end="1657">We'll build this dashboard together</h1>
<p data-start="1659" data-end="1731">Instead of just telling you to "make charts," I'll tell you <strong data-start="1719" data-end="1730">exactly</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="1733" data-end="1868">
